{"tid":2299633,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"「hr悲歌」25歲求職男突抓狂...尖刀割爆「面試官」喉嚨！他倒臥血泊當場慘死","createTime":"2020-11-25T02:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T20:20:27.000Z","uid":33359,"like":71,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"92437934ecd84c67f6af0dc4cdb80863f8e7aeec","tid":2299633,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1860553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%253Fnews_id%253D1860553&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=187ef576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1860553</a><br />\n<br />\n記者蔡儀潔／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n廣東深圳一家科技公司日前發生死亡命案，25歲的李姓求職男子在面試期間，突然持刀將26歲的白姓男經理割喉殺害，隨即逃離現場，死者則倒臥血泊，畫面相當駭人！<br />\n<br />\n綜合陸媒報導，事發於18日下午4時左右，深圳市龍華區展濤科技大廈C座一家公司內，一名面試人員把面試官割喉殺害後逃跑。同事發現後立刻撥打120，可惜救護人員到場時，面試官已失血過多不治身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目擊者透露，當時面試官和應聘者在一間會議室面試，應聘者逃跑後，面試官才跑出來滿身是血，然後躺在血泊中。警方隨後也到達現場展開調查，原來兩人是前同事，李男因個人矛盾積怨而行兇，目前李某已投案，案件在進一步偵辦中。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後引發熱議，不少人聽後表示「脖子一涼」，「同一棟樓，嚇得廁所都不敢去」、「太可怕了吧這」、「前同事...這人應聘就是為了殺人嗎&hellip;&hellip;」、「得饒人處且饒人」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇吓你班hr仲敢唔敢審犯咁審<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b3a9c2f2bb7638c4656002c7974b05ca782f70","tid":2299633,"uid":25260,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:51:38.000Z","msg":"慘死師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a3be0954a0afa07efbe7a66117aa03bca07ac2","tid":2299633,"uid":207702,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />觀塘"},{"pid":"6e077baa9303188bae61c824ecb03aff9e970885","tid":2299633,"uid":282884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"gif呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26728ae32673ac5dbe92a786f9320bb41e44d35e","tid":2299633,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:52:28.000Z","msg":"有冇片睇"},{"pid":"4b7097903a88780d3d6136273508a9902a3e8d7f","tid":2299633,"uid":113259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:52:33.000Z","msg":"鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b8dbb6a045e717ebc7e8ecdcc26e3e471a527b","tid":2299633,"uid":11291,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"放心香港公司果班濕鳩HR會繼續審犯咁問人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2001bee5ddfbf2c20ac8898a8416d2f4d65389","tid":2299633,"uid":317378,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:52:38.000Z","msg":"帶刀去見工，好有覺悟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc5fed7ee466057e9a15d44d956b6651f644812","tid":2299633,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"26歲做經理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 25歲見工 <br />\n肯定串柒柒先俾人殺死"},{"pid":"d9ea498813f4c39269c5d88fec706ea71ddfb477","tid":2299633,"uid":208336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:53:06.000Z","msg":"係咪你黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae5da6eca5664344a2e930f56c8925e3e9208c3","tid":2299633,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:53:25.000Z","msg":"HR師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2eb73c5afb6c9fcd79191142ea5f4a68860b1b9","tid":2299633,"uid":383632,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:54:47.000Z","msg":"失血師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid